{"tid":1908801,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲方力申再戰泳壇　宣布花1年半力衝明年世錦賽","createTime":"2020-03-03T13:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T18:00:35.000Z","uid":105567,"like":32,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7f83ed1474f953297f88b6aa7cc07e9fd8f5eb","tid":1908801,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"方力申（Alex）去年順利挑戰45公里環島泳，為自己游泳生涯再添紀錄。然而「飛魚王子」也許會重現室內賽。昨日（2日）他於社交媒體上宣布，或會參戰明年的先進組世界游泳錦標賽，定下練水的新目標。<br />\n<br />\n縱使退役近16年，方力申仍未忘游泳的樂趣。去年在香港環島泳45公里慈善挑戰，他更以10小時43分06秒完成，打破英國泳手保持的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n近日剛度過40歲生日的Alex，亦一直保持練水習慣，昨日他在社交媒體Instagram宣布，游泳生涯延續的可能：「明年的World Masters Championship （先進組世界游泳錦標賽）可能就是我現在繼續練水的目標！」<br />\n<br />\n先進組世錦賽雖有「先進組」之名，但事實上年過25歲已可參加，去年亦有年逾90的泳手參賽。未現身世界級賽事，方力申也直言存在未知數，但對於明年日本舉行的先進組世錦賽，定必坐言起行：「衝前三名是我再上一級的目標。可是，還有一年半的時間，對於一個成年人來說，存在太多變數了；做到與否，我不知道；但現在不開始，到時就一定做不到！」<br />\n<br />\n方力申曾持有9項香港紀錄，至今仍有兩項未有人打破。2000年悉尼奧運，他出戰200背及400米個人混合泳，均刷新香港紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4093361/org/7be6aca116a313654f719b7d704ad80c.png/626dvOM9GWaVcNGAOGmtYkQlM2EBpiC7AGKYxgBimMY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4093361%2Forg%2F7be6aca116a313654f719b7d704ad80c.png%2F626dvOM9GWaVcNGAOGmtYkQlM2EBpiC7AGKYxgBimMY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=32539971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/442709/%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3-40%E6%AD%B2%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%B3%E5%86%8D%E6%88%B0%E6%B3%B3%E5%A3%87-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%8A%B11%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%9D%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E9%8C%A6%E8%B3%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F442709%2F%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%25B3%25B3-40%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E5%25A3%2587-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%258A%25B11%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2596%25E9%258C%25A6%25E8%25B3%25BD&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4f1df07d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/442709/%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3-40%E6%AD%B2%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%B3%E5%86%8D%E6%88%B0%E6%B3%B3%E5%A3%87-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%8A%B11%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%9D%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E9%8C%A6%E8%B3%BD</a>"},{"pid":"4f163e8b9c1b9ef2b2f4fcfa24a05db86d917777","tid":1908801,"uid":143151,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"Ching 發現你次次出post 都貼埋藍底報link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f99e52ce10bb63b58974860254a77c41889c95","tid":1908801,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"我屌sa你哋班YellowNazi老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1907722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1907722</a>"},{"pid":"bb879df3b275945b9925f4d71f4239d82ebe1699","tid":1908801,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"68ad70346bce45c9ab62ca447305aff4e3ed045c","tid":1908801,"uid":22700,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"同屎塔飛散左之後佢就不斷搵目標去衝"},{"pid":"8bea5e34041eed74db6f37297f98f8cd7062b14a","tid":1908801,"uid":85839,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"運動員係要有火"},{"pid":"4a9e2aa80ed9c0aafb590275236930a019eb7986","tid":1908801,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"旅發局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebc6ff3feb94d00e11dbe920237a9c1465e275c","tid":1908801,"uid":99725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:21:17.0